title: Megawati Respons Surya Paloh Soal Omongan Partai Sombong, Ini Penjelasannya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Akhirnya Megawati Soekarnoputri menjawab terkait sindiran soal partai sombong yang sempat dilontarkan Ketum Partai Nasdem Surya Paloh.||||Ketua Umum PDIP menegaskan dirinya tak pernah menjelek-jelekkan partai politik mana pun.||||"Karena ada juga yang mengatakan 'ada sebuah partai sombong sekali'. Lah piye, kok dibilang sombong, emangnya kenapa,"kata Megawati.||||Megawati juga menegaskan tidak pernah menjelekkan partai mana pun. ||||Baca Juga Megawati Jengkel Dibilang Retak dengan Jokowi: Ngamuk Ajah Gak Pernah! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301257/megawati-jengkel-dibilang-retak-dengan-jokowi-ngamuk-ajah-gak-pernah||||"Tidak pernah menjelekkan ketua apa pun. Saya berjalan sendiri membentuk partai saya yang saya hormati dan sayangi yang bernama Partai Demokrasi Indonesia Perjuangan. Jangan, jangan, negeri ini harus dibangun dengan bersatu," imbuhnya.||||Sebelumnya perihal partai sombong pernah disampaikan Surya Paloh saat penutupan Rakernas NasDem di JCC, Jakarta.||||"Kami menjaga komunikasi kepada seluruh komponen masyarakat secara lebih bijak, secara lebih luwes. Jadi buang itu praktik kesombongan, merasa hebat sendiri, merasa paling mantap sendiri, itu bukan NasDem. Ada urusan apa? Tapi kalau ada yang bersalah sangka kepada kami, maka kami harus arif dan bijaksana. NasDem masih banyak stok senyumnya. dan berpolitik dengan sukaria," kata Surya Paloh, Jumat (17/6/2022).||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301270/megawati-respons-surya-paloh-soal-omongan-partai-sombong-ini-penjelasannya

title: US ban on imports from China's Xinjiang takes effect
description: A US ban on all imports of goods made in China's Xinjiang region is due to come into force today. ||It is a major exporter of cotton and tomatoes, but is also where Uighurs and other Muslim groups are being held in detention camps.||There are concerns that it could cause further problems to the global supply chain.||The ban intensifies pressure on Beijing over allegations of rights violations that took place at Xinjiang region against Muslim Uyghur and other minorities. ||China denies the claims and has warned of retaliatory measures.||||Al Jazeeraâ€™s Katrina Yu reports from Beijing, China.||||- Subscribe to our channel: http://aje.io/AJSubscribe ||- Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/AJEnglish ||- Find us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/aljazeera ||- Check our website: https://www.aljazeera.com/||||#USChinaTensions #XinjiangBan #Uighurs

title: New details revealed in murder of Filipino lawyer in Philadelphia
description: The mother of a Filipino lawyer is demanding justice after a shooting in Philadelphia left her son dead over the weekend.|It happened around 4 a.m. Saturday near 38th and Spruce streets. Officials say John Albert Laylo, 35, and his mother, Leah Laylo, were in an Uber on the way to Philadelphia International Airport. The pair had been in the city visiting family since June 9.|Leah Laylo soon found herself under a hail of bullets.|"I just heard the window on my right side shatter, and when I looked at my son, John, he was bleeding," she said.|Police say the gunman, who investigators believe was in a black vehicle, came up from behind and fired several rounds into the car. The gunman then pulled up on the driver's side of the car and fired additional gunshots.|John was shot in the head and died from his injuries Sunday. His mother was injured by glass fragments.|Sources tell Action News that investigators are reviewing video that may prove the shooter targeted the wrong car. Police sources also say the shooter may have been in a black Cadillac.|#philadelphia #shooting #philippines |READ MORE: https://6abc.com/john-albert-laylo-murder-philadelphia-pa-shooting-philippines-lawyer-killed-38th-spruce-street/11981806/

title: See Why Japan is the Most Disciplined Team in Volleyball History !!!
description: See Why Japan is the Most Disciplined Team in Volleyball History !!! Men's volleyball team Japan is currently one of the best teams in the volleyball nations league 2022. In this video you can see why japan is one of the most disciplined teams in the world. Japan is a team that fights and never gives up, and that can be seen in their incredible defense. It remains to be seen how this great team will perform in the upcoming part of the Men's VNL 2022.|The Japan men's national volleyball team represents Japan in international volleyball competitions and friendly matches. Their nickname is "RYUJIN NIPPON (é¾ç¥ NIPPON) ", meaning "Japanese Dragon God" or "Dragon God of Japan" in Japanese. Japan won a bronze medal at the Tokyo 1964 Olympic Games, followed by silver at Mexico 1968 and a gold at Munich 1972. The years after this have been less successful. Japan missed three successive Olympic Games before returning at Beijing 2008, where they failed to win a match. Japan then failed to qualify for the London 2012 Olympic Games and also missed Rio 2016 after finishing seventh at the World Olympic Qualification Tournament in Tokyo.|They also failed to qualify for the 2014 FIVB World Championship the first edition they had missed in 54 years. They had previously won FIVB World Championship bronze medals in 1970 and 1974. Japan silver medalists at the 1969 and 1977 World Cup. Japan has been less successful in the World League era. title: Momen Ganjar dan Bambang Pacul Salam Komando Disorak Para Kader di Acara Rakernas
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  - PDIP menggelar rakernas bersama para kader untuk mendengarkan arahan Ketum Megawati Soekarnoputri. ||||Sebelum acara dimulai etua Badan Pemenangan Pemilu (Bappilu) PDIP Bambang Wuryanto atau akrab disapa Bambang Pacul menyapa para kader di ruangan. ||||Tiba Bambang ke arah depan dekat dengan posisi Ganjar Pranowo. ||||Sontak Ganjar pun berdiri menyodorkan tangan lebih dulu untuk bersalaman dengan Bambang Pacul.||||Baca Juga Tanggapan Ganjar Atas Pernyataan Bambang Pacul di https://www.kompas.tv/article/221200/tanggapan-ganjar-atas-pernyataan-bambang-pacul||||Tak lama setelah itu keduanya kembali bersalaman hingga menyambut sorak pada kader lainnya. ||||Sebelumnya  Bambang Pacul kerap melontarkan kritikan terhadap Ganjar Pranowo.||||Elektabilitas Ganjar di sejumlah lembaga survei pun juga sering disebut-sebut menjadi nama kuat untuk Capres 2024 ketimbang nama Puan Maharani. ||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301133/momen-ganjar-dan-bambang-pacul-salaman-disorak-para-kader-di-acara-rakernas

title: Momen Jokowi Tertawa Dengar Cerita Lucu Megawati di Raker PDIP soal Teriak Merdeka
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Presiden Joko Widodo atau Jokowi tertawa mendengar cerita lucu Ketua Umum Megawati Soekarnoputri soal teriakan merdeka.||||Suasana tersebut nampak saat Megawati membuka Rakernas PDIP, Selasa (21/6).||||"Pak Jokowi supaya tahu, kemarin saya diundang untuk memberikan arahan di Angkatan Laut. Supaya bapak Presiden tahu, itu ketika saya teriak-teriak merdeka, media-media dan banyak orang 'udah merdeka kok terus teriak-teriak merdeka?'" kisah Mega pada Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Presiden Jokowi Hadiri Rakernas PDIP di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301098/presiden-jokowi-hadiri-rakernas-pdip||||"Jadi saya bilang, ya itu maunya saya. Tapi untuk mengingatkan, meski kita telah merdeka, bukan berarti kita lupa kita orang yang bebas dan berdaulat," lanjut Mega diiringi tepuk tangan hadirin.||||Lalu Megawati bercerita momen-momen saat dia mengajak prajurit AL berteriak merdeka, dan hanya sedikit yang mengikutinya.||||"Waktu saya teriak merdeka, hanya berapa orang. Saya bilang kurang,"||||"Saya merdeka lagi, agak banyak. Jangan lupa, saya ini pernah panglima tertinggi.," kata Megawati disambut tawa tamu Rakernas PDIP termasuk Presiden Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Megawati Resmikan Kapal Perang Bernama KRI Bung Karno di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300986/megawati-resmikan-kapal-perang-bernama-kri-bung-karno||||Kisah lucu tersebut disampaikan Megawati kala dirinya berbicara membuka Rakernas PDIP yang digelar Selasa (21/6).||||Sejumlah petinggi PDIP hadir, termasuk ketua DPP PDIP Puan Maharani yang duduk di samping Presiden Jokowi.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301136/momen-jokowi-tertawa-dengar-cerita-lucu-megawati-di-raker-pdip-soal-teriak-merdeka

title: â€˜Selective Religiophobiaâ€™: India calls out Kabul Gurdwara â€˜hate crimeâ€™ at UN
description: In a strong worded statement on the Kabul Gurdwara attack, India called out selectivism in condemning hatred against non-abrahamic religions at the United Nations. Speaking at the United Nations General Assembly (UNGA), India's Permanent Representative of India to the United Nations, Ambassador TS Tirumurti raised concerns about the 'selective' efforts to combat religiophobias. "And on 18th June, a couple of days ago and on the very day we commemorated the International Day for countering hate speech, we saw yet another tragic example of this against Sikh religion, this time in Kabul, Afghanistan. The Gurudwara Karte Parwan was attacked, desecrated and damaged. We condemn in the strongest terms this cowardly dastardly attack where lives were tragically lost," said Tirumurti at the informal High-Level Meeting to mark the commemoration of the first International Day for Countering Hate Speech. description: President Biden says he is considering a federal gas tax holiday, which could save consumers just over 18 cents a gallon. title: Nova Scotia mass shooting: Video shows the moment RCMP officers killed gunman Gabriel Wortman
description: WARNING: Video contains disturbing content and is not suitable for all viewers. Viewer discretion is advised.|Videos of Nova Scotia RCMP officers fatally shooting the perpetrator of one of the worst mass killings in Canadian history have been released to the public.|The decision Monday from the commissioners of a public inquiry into the 2020 Nova Scotia mass shooting reversed their previous decision to shield the videos from publication.|The five videos from various security cameras at an Irving Big Stop gas station in Enfield, N.S., were recorded when RCMP officers killed the gunman on April 19, 2020, ending a 13-hour rampage that claimed 22 lives.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8934174/videos-rcmp-killing-ns-shooter-released/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #novascotia #novascotiashooting #nsshooting #rcmp #mcc

title: Steph Curry an All-Time Great with 4th Finals win? Ryen Russillo on Kyrie vs. Nets, Tatum | THE HERD
description: Ryen Russillo joins Colin Cowherd on The Herd to insist he's not bitter after this Boston Celtics lost the NBA Finals to Stephen Curry and the Golden State Warriors. title: President Joe Biden considers federal gas tax holiday to reduce prices
description: President Joe Biden is considering a federal gas tax holiday to reduce prices.  Right now, drivers in Metro Detroit are paying an average of $5.26 per gallon.  Suspending the federal gas tax would drop prices by about 18 cents per gallon, putting prices at around $5.08, which is still pretty high but is better for the consumer.

title: Prime Time With Ravish Kumar: Army Begins Agniveer Hiring Process
description: Prime Time With Ravish Kumar - June 20, 2022: The Indian Army today issued a notification that the registration under the 'Agnipath' military defence scheme will start next month. The 'Agnipath' scheme, which was unveiled by the government last week, aims to bring in men and women between the ages of 17-and-a-half and 21 into the armed forces for a four-year tenure. The BJP has come under fire with hundreds of potential recruits protesting against the shorter tenure. Amid the rising demands for the scrapping of the newly launched Agnipath recruitment scheme for the military, a senior Army officer on Sunday clarified that the programme will not be rolled back. title: Modi Govt's 'Agnipath' gets Corporate India's support; Tata Sons, Biocon, Goenkas back scheme
description: After Anand Mahindra, N Chandrasekaran, the Tata Sons Chairman, backed Modi government's Agnipath scheme amid protests. He said Agnipath will make available a very disciplined youth for the industry, including the Tata Group. Harsh Goenka, chairman of Rama Prasad Goenka Group, also spoke in support of Agnipath. Kiran Mazumdar-Shaw, Executive Chairperson of Biocon Ltd, also lent her support to the scheme. Earlier, industrialist Anand Mahindra made an offer to employ 'Agniveers' in the Mahindra group. title: Building 21st century road network to power India's development
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi laid the foundation stone of two sections of the Bengaluru Ring Road project.  The project to be developed at a cost of more than Rs 2280 crore will help reduce traffic congestion in the city. Prime Minister also laid the foundation stone of various other road projects : six laning of Nelamangala-Tumkur section of NH-48; widening of Punjalkatte-Charmadi section of NH-73; rehabilitation and upgradation of a section of NH-69. The cumulative cost to be incurred in these projects is about Rs 3150 crore. Prime Minister laid the foundation stone of Multi Modal Logistics Park, which is being developed at Muddalinganahalli, about 40 km from Bengaluru at a cost of about Rs 1800 crore. From the lighting, camera movement, and long takes, everything about Euphoriaâ€™s cinematography is designed to capture â€œemotional realism.â€ In this video, weâ€™re going to look inside these elements to see just how this is achieved.|Euphoria Cinematography Lighting|The lighting in Euphoria is both dynamic and colorful, intended to highlight the heightened emotions of the characters. Most of the time, bold primary colors are used. And in some cases, the mixing of colors enhances the effect. For example, nighttime lighting blends blueish moonlight with warm yellow tungsten streetlights. And during the second season, the decision was made to shoot on film, which further enhanced the color palettes. Thatâ€™s why the cinematography of Euphoria Season 2 looks so different from the first season.|Euphoria Cinematography Camera Movement|Camera movement is also a huge part of the overall Euphoria cinematography. As cinematographer Marcell RÃ©v explains, the moving camera brought a certain energy that ties the different storylines together. Not only is the camera as active as the characters, but it also brings us directly into their mental state. Consider the moment in the pilot as the hallway literally spins around Rue as she experiences an â€œaltered state.â€|Euphoria Cinematography Long Takes|The final key element bringing all of the Euphoria cinematography together is the use of long takes. Often these long takes move in and out of rooms, connecting characters in a single shot and creating unity between all of their experiences. title: Hati-Hati, Penipuan Modus Baru yang Bisa Menguras Rekeningmu dalam 5 Menit!
description: KOMPAS.TV-Awas modus begal rekening yang bisa menguras rekening dalam 5 menit.||||Teknologi yang semakin maju terkadang juga memberi dampak buruk bagi masyarakat.||||Contohnya seperti yang sedang marak saat ini, yakni penipuan dengan modus social engineering atau soceng.||||Si penipu berpura-pura menjadi petugas bank, namun bertanya password, PIN, MPIN, OTP, atau data pribadi.||||Bahkan mereka bisa menghubungi korban melalui akun email, website bank, telepon, dan akun media sosial.||||Otoritas Jasa Keuangan (OJK) mengimbau masyarakat, untuk waspada terhadap penipuan bermodus soceng ini.||||Melansir akun instagram resmi Otoritas Jasa Keuangan. Berikut modus penipuan social engineering atau soceng yang harus kamu ketahui:||||Menawarkan Jadi Agen Laku Pandai||||Mereka tidak memberikan syarat yang rumit, dan meminta korban mentransfer uang untuk mendapat mesin EDC.||||Informasi Perubahan Biaya Transfer||||Penipu akan berpura-pura jadi petugas bank, lalu kamu akan diperintah mengisi tautan yang meminta data pribadi.||||Tawaran Nasabah Prioritas||||Pelaku akan berbohong dengan menawarkan iklan upgrade menjadi nasabah prioritas dengan rayuan manis berkedok promosi.||||Akun Layanan Konsumen Palsu||||Akun palsu ini muncul saat konsumen mengeluh mengenai layanan perbankan, kemudian penipu akan menawarkan bantuan, dengan mengarahkan ke website palsu yang meminta data pribadi.||||Baca Juga 4 Poin Penting Aturan Baru OJK: Debt Collector Tak Boleh Seenaknya, Ancaman Masuk Delik Pidana di https://www.kompas.tv/article/291792/4-poin-penting-aturan-baru-ojk-debt-collector-tak-boleh-seenaknya-ancaman-masuk-delik-pidana||||Editor Video & Grafis: Joshua Victor ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300975/hati-hati-penipuan-modus-baru-yang-bisa-menguras-rekeningmu-dalam-5-menit

title: Leftist Gustavo Petro wins Colombia's presidential election | DW News
description: Leftist presidential candidate Gustavo Petro wins Colombia's election by a narrow margin. The former guerilla and current senator will be Colombia's first leftist leader. He's edged out his opponent, former mayor and millionare Rodolfo Hernandez. title: EXPOSED: The shocking lengths truck drivers take to meet deadlines | 60 Minutes Australia
description: Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | Highway to Hell (2005)|If you're like us, just the thought of a huge semi looming up ahead on the highway is unnerving.  And there's every reason to be wary, even downright scared.  It's a fact that most truckies break the rules.  They speed, they're doped to the eyeballs, they drive till they drop. And their bosses not only allow this lawlessness, many expect it.  During the course of this investigation, we tailed one driver, who was at the wheel for 22 solid hours. That's illegal and so were the speeds he clocked up.  So you really have to ask how many more innocent people have to die before these blokes get the message.|WATCH more of 60 Minutes Australia: https://www.60minutes.com.au |LIKE 60 Minutes Australia on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/60Minutes9 |FOLLOW 60 Minutes Australia on Twitter: https://twitter.com/60Mins |FOLLOW 60 Minutes Australia on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/60minutes9|For forty years, 60 Minutes have been telling Australians the worldâ€™s greatest stories. title: Penampakan Spanduk Foto Anies Baswedan Bareng Presiden RI yang Dicopot Satpol PP
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Inilah spanduk yang dibentangkan di atas Jembatan Penyebrangan Orang (JPO) di Pulogadung, Jakarta Timur.||||Nampak di spanduk tersebut menampilkan foto Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan yang disandingkan bersama foto seluruh Presiden Republik Indonesia.||||Foto Anies Baswedan terlihat berada diurutan ke delapan tepatnya disamping foto presiden Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Ini 3 Nama Diusulkan Nasdem jadi Capres 2024: Anies, Andika Perkasa, Ganjar di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300232/ini-3-nama-diusulkan-nasdem-jadi-capres-2024-anies-andika-perkasa-ganjar||||Belum diketahui siapa yang memasang spanduk tersebut. Namun diduga spanduk ini baru dipasang lantaran warna spanduk belum kusam.||||Sementara itu, petugas Satpol PP Kelurahan Rawamangun yang tiba di lokasi langsung melakukan penertiban dengan mencopot spanduk tersebut.||||Penertiban dilakukan karena tidak berizin dan melanggar perda DKI Jakarta nomor 8 tahun 2007 tentang ketertiban umum.||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300834/penampakan-spanduk-foto-anies-baswedan-bareng-presiden-ri-yang-dicopot-satpol-pp

title: Big crackdown over 'Agnipath' violence as over 1,500 booked; Forces bar entry for 'arsonists'
description: Big crackdown by govt after violent protests across states over 'Agnipath' scheme. Over 1,500 protesters have been booked while hundreds of FIRs have been filed in several states. 805 people have been booked in Bihar, from where these protests started after the announcement of the scheme. The Ministry of Home Affairs have also banned 35 Whatsapp groups for spreading fake news over 'Agnipath'. The action comes as the defence ministry has declared that there is no place for 'arsonists' in the forces. title: Watch: Cop, Wife On Scooter Swallowed By Drain On Waterlogged UP Road
description: A policeman and his wife escaped with injuries after their two-wheeler fell headlong into a drain inundated with rainwater in Uttar Pradesh's Aligarh. The cop, with his wife riding pillion, was going to a hospital in Aligarh. The video from the accident site shows the cop navigating the waterlogged road. The front wheel hits something, and the couple is catapulted into the drain water. title: SMRC: Ganjar Paling Potensial Angkat Suara Nasdem
description: Peta koalisi jelang Pemilu 2024 masih sangat dinamis. Nantinya akan ada sejumlah poros koalisi yang bakal meramaikan hajatan lima tahunan, demi memenuhi syarat untuk mengusung Capres dan Cawapres di Pilpres 2024 nanti. Lalu bagaimana lembaga survei SMRC membaca konstelasi terkini menuju 2024. Iqbal Kurniadi akan membahasnya dalam wawancara via zoom bersama Saidiman Ahmad selaku Peneliti SMRC.

title: Polisi Olah TKP Kasus Tewas Anggota Brimob di Jayawijaya, Diserang Usai Tembak Sapi
description: JAYAWIJAYA, KOMPAS.TV - Polres Jayawijaya melakukan olah tempat kejadian perkara (TKP) dengan menghadirkan saksi dalam kasus pembunuhan Bripda Diego Rumaropen, personel Brimob Yon D Wamena di Napua, Wamena, Kabupaten Jayawijaya.||||Dalam olah TKP ini polisi menghadirkan saksi pemilik sapi, pembeli sapi termasuk ketiga saksi lainya ada saat insiden tersebut.||||Hasil dari olah TKP ini polisi akan dikumpulkan dan dicocokan barang bukti dilokasi kejadian untuk ditingkatkan ke penyidik.||||Dalam penyelidikannya, polisi menduga pelaku pembacokan dan perampasan senjata api di lokasi kejadian berjumlah 2 orang.||||Baca Juga Polisi Gelar Olah TKP Kasus Tewasnya Anggota Brimob di Papua, 5 Saksi Dihadirkan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300748/polisi-gelar-olah-tkp-kasus-tewasnya-anggota-brimob-di-papua-5-saksi-dihadirkan||||Berdasarkan kronologi yang diterima, menyebutkan korban bersama Danki Brimob Yon D Wamena, AKP R ditelepon oleh saudara AM untuk membantunya  menembak sapi milik AM di Napua.||||Kemudian, AKP R mengajak Bripda Diego Rumaropen ke lokasi kejadian. AKP R membawa 1 pucuk senjata api sniper styer dan bripda Diego membawa senjata api ak 101.||||Pukul 15.20 WIT, setelah sapi ditembak oleh AKP R, lalu AKP R menitip senjata api yang digunakan untuk menembak sapi ke Bripda Diego karena mau mengecek sapi tersebut.||||Sesaat setelah ditinggalkan AKP Rustam, korban didatangi 2 orang dengan menggunakan parang dan membacok Bripda Diego, lalu mengambil 2 pucuk senjata api dan melarikan diri.||||Atas peristiwa ini polisi terus mengejar pelaku pembunuhan dan perampasan 2 pucuk senjata.||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300763/polisi-olah-tkp-kasus-tewas-anggota-brimob-di-jayawijaya-diserang-usai-tembak-sapi

title: Protesters detained in India after violent clash over new military recruitment scheme
description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|Protesters in India have clashed with police during rallies against a new military recruitment scheme. Dozens of people were detained on June 19, 2022, as police used batons and tear gas to disperse protesters who had taken to the streets and damaged government buildings to protest against the policy. The scheme announced June 14 calls for young adults to be admitted into the armed forces for a period of four years and 75 per cent of the recruits taken in from 2022 must retire after their terms with no pension benefits. The new plan is a major departure from the past when military service was usually seen as a lifetime job, and comes as the nationâ€™s unemployment rate is at its worst level since the 1970s.|Related story:|Indian trains set ablaze in protests against military hiring changes https://sc.mp/mclj|Support us:|https://subscribe.scmp.com|Follow us on:|Website:  https://www.scmp.com|Facebook:  https://facebook.com/scmp|Twitter:  https://twitter.com/scmpnews|Instagram:  https://instagram.com/scmpnews|Linkedin:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-china-morning-post/|#scmp #Asia #India

description: World swimmingâ€™s governing body has effectively banned transgender athletes from competing in womenâ€™s elite races.|FINA voted to stop any person who has transitioned from competing in the events, if they have been through any stage of male puberty.  |They are aiming to establish a new â€œopenâ€ category of competition for swimmers whose gender identity is different from their biological sex.|The new policy, which was passed with 71% of the vote of FINA members, was described as "only a first step towards full inclusion" for transgender athletes.|The former Great Britain swimmer Sharron Davies, who has argued against transgender participation in women's elite swimming, said she was "really proud of FINA".|However Athlete Ally, an LGBT advocacy group, called the new policy "discriminatory and harmfulâ€. |Huw Edwards presents BBC News at Ten reporting by sports correspondent Jane Dougall. |Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: I'm Shipping My Shelby GT500 to the UK, FINALLY!
description: The time has arrived for my Shelby GT500 to go home! After owning the American Shmeemobile for 18 months, it is now the right moment to pack it up to send it to the UK and onwards to @The Shmuseum! Join me for the last drive in the USA and to send it on the way.|I tracked down my beastly Mustang on Auto Tempest at the start of 2021, took delivery of it at Ikonick Motors, then promptly installed SunTek Reaction PPF and fitted the Altered Black PPF stripes. It didn't take long to get on the road, before a 6 week adventure across the country all the way to LA with countless amazing stops and moments along the way. Since then, it has been based in Miami and popped up from time to time for various journeys, until this last month with the stops around New York before @Gumball 3000 brought us all the way back from Toronto to Miami.|Now though, with over 12,000 miles on the clock it is time to get it home at long last, to get the car dropped off for transport and all the registration with MyCarImport to get it onto UK soil and officially registered as SH67 MEE. For now that means cleaning it and preparing it for travel, with a few items boxed up including the spare wheels, and some other items to go through in due course.|However, before that, let's visit DuPontRegistry's new customer supercar experience for a soft preview of things to come and a look at some fantastic cars. The display includes a Lamborghini Sian Roadster, Essenza SC V12, a Porsche Carrera GT in Ferrari's Rosso Fuoco paint, an Aventador SVJ paint matched to the red sole of a Louboutin shoe, and plenty more.|It's then time for the road, and the very final drive in the USA, ensuring that the car is out of gas and ready for the sailing which will take 1-2 months to get to the UK, before the import process begins which in all will take about the same. I believe it should be 'good to go' somewhere around September, but let's see!|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:31 Preparing for Transport|04:41 Entering Supercar Heaven|06:13 DuPont Registry Experience|12:35 Washing the GT500|13:25 The Last Drive|23:06 Final Goodbye|25:24 Wrap Up|#Shelby #GT500 #DuPontRegistry|||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Cerita Chairul Tanjung Diberi Kado Oleh Ridwan Kamil Saat Bertakziah Ke Pakuan
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Chairul Tanjung bersama sang Istri dan anaknya datang ke Gedung Pakuan  untuk menyampaikan bela sungkawa kepada keluarga Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil. title: Are They All The Same Motor Oil? Let's Settle This!  Four Levels of Pennzoil Motor Oil Compared
description: Let's find out if Pennzoil's motor oil (Pennzoil Synthetic Blend, Pennzoil Full Synthetic, Pennzoil Platinum and Pennzoil Ultra Platinum) are basically the oil.  All four oils tested sent to an independent oil lab for oil analysis. I tested oils for evaporative loss, lubricity or film strength, cold oil flow both new oil and after exposure to heat.  Additionally, in a final test, Pennzoil Ultra Platinum is exposed to 10% gasoline and another sample is exposed to antifreeze to see the impact it has on lubricity or oil performance. title: Govt won't rollback 'Agnipath', says 'no place for arsonists in forces' amid widespread protests
description: The defence ministry has made its stand clear on the 'Agnipath' scheme. There will be no rollback despite raging protests across states. Top defence officials said that the reforms like Agnipath was long pending as the armed forces wanted to bring youthfulness and experience. It also warned the arsonists as protests over the scheme goes violent in several parts of the country. The Additional Secy of the Department for Military Affairs Lt.General Puri said that there is no space for indiscipline in the forces and aspirants have to pledge in enrollment form that they were not involved in arson. He further added that if during police verification, an FIR against the candidate is found then they simply can't join. title: BREAKING: Hubble Just Made A Stunning Black Hole Discovery
description: While everyone's waiting for the first images of the James Webb Space Telescope, Hubble continues to make stunning astronomical discoveries. The Hubble Space Telescope has determined the mass of the first free-floating black hole in our Galaxy. The Milky Way is believed to be home to more than 100 million stellar-mass black holes. However, the problem is that since even light cannot escape the gravity of a black hole, it is impossible to discover them. So far, astronomers had only discovered black holes in binary systems by analyzing either the gravitational waves or electromagnetic radiation emitted when they feast on their companion stars.|But now, using the technique of gravitational microlensing and Hubble's meticulous observations, two teams of researchers have found the first evidence of a rogue black hole in our galaxy.|All Episodes Of The Series: https://bit.ly/369kG4p|Basics of Astrophysics series: https://bit.ly/3xII54M|REFERENCES:|Research Paper of the Berkeley Team: https://bit.ly/39CluAV|Research Paper of the  STScI Team: https://bit.ly/3bcoCUl|Earendel Episode of this series: https://bit.ly/3QsayXj|Roman Space Telescope: https://go.nasa.gov/3xAgfd3|Created By: Rishabh Nakra|Narrated By: Jeffrey Smith|The Secrets of the Universe on the internet:|Website: https://bit.ly/sou_website|Facebook: https://bit.ly/sou_fb|Instagram: https://bit.ly/sou_ig|Twitter: https://bit.ly/sou_twitter

title: The rise of a global company -  From the microscope to the moon landing | DW Documentary
description: 175 years ago, the young mechanic Carl Zeiss opened a small workshop for precision mechanics and optics. These humble beginnings in the German city of Jena were the foundation of the Zeiss technology company, which today operates worldwide.|The production of glass with game-changing optical properties was one of the developments that helped Carl Zeiss create a company that valued scientific research highly, while never forgetting scienceâ€™s social impact. |Zeiss microscopes have been used by more than 30 Nobel Prize winners. To this day, these instruments offer unrivaled image resolution, with lenses that can display structures one thousand times smaller than a human hair. Light microscopes allow living cells to be examined with extreme gentleness and speed, as well.|The Zeiss company was involved in the moon landing in 1969, and thus helped redefine the limits of what humans are capable of. Images of the historic event were captured using Zeiss camera lenses developed specially for space. These lenses were key to the later development of photolithography, which plays a decisive role in the production of microchips. Developments in extreme ultraviolet lithography led to Zeiss winning the German Future Prize together with the Fraunhofer Institute and the Trumpf company.|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: How I Transformed My Lawn WITHOUT A Complete Renovation
description: Let's go back in time and show you where I started with my front lawn, all the way to what it looks like today! |It's been quite the journey from what my front lawn looked like in 2011 to what it looks like today. I thought it might be fun to go down memory lane and show you how the journey progressed through the years and how I did this without ever spraying out the original yard and starting over completely or doing a complete lawn renovation.  There has been plenty of lawn renovation work over the years but not in the traditional sense. title: He saved stone barn. Also built unreal villa under hillside
description: Gorka Ibargoyen bought an abandoned stone housebarn in the Bera Valley of Navarra and wanted to expand it to fit large gatherings without destroying the original character. With the help of architect friend Jordi Hidalgo TanÃ© he went underground, building an annex to the primary home inside the adjacent hillside. Accessible via an all-glass corridor the addition is nearly invisible.|The cave-like addition resembles a fissure in a mountain, and that is what inspired TanÃ©â€™s design, and is nearly invisible from the outside: it is accessible via a transparent, all-glass corridor. When looking at the model, Ibargoyen feared the hidden home might resemble a bunker, but the glass skylight in the green roof light combined with the long window running down the entire length of the structure brings in plenty of daylight to the subterranean shelter.|To unify the two structures, the used only glass, concrete, and wood for the interior, resulting in a concrete sink and a wooden shower. While the result is modern elegance, Ibargoyen insists itâ€™s not a fussy home â€œThings are made to be used, and to show wear over timeâ€, he explains and pointing to a wine stain on the cement countertop, he adds, â€œThat is happinessâ€.|https://www.landaburuborda.com/|On *faircompanies https://faircompanies.com/videos/he-saved-stone-barn-also-built-unreal-villa-under-hillside/
